name: SUBMERMAN
description:
Classic Creature #2

SUBMERMAN was fashioned in the murky depths of man's madness: glistening, sharp, dripping. It lurks in the deepest waters of a human's mortal fears, and feasts upon the guppies of the soul. Inescapable as the dare-to-be-tread deep of the psyche is the SUBMERMAN's local Saturday hangout spot. 


Created in VR, Finished in 3D.
